Jonathan Wrather https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Wrather 0 Jonathan Paul Wrather (born 16 March 1969) is an English actor and editor. He is known for his soap opera roles in Coronation Street as Joe Carter from 2002 until 2003, and in Emmerdale as Pierce Harris from 2016 until 2017.
